Description:
Multiplayer map inspired by [url=https://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=2142821184]FroYo's Minigolf[/url].  There are 9 levels, all centered around air dribbling.  Play 1v1, 2v2, 3v3, or 4v4.

Settings
- Match Length: Unlimited
- Boost Amount: Unlimited

Spawn ordering
- Spawn 1: offensive
- Spawn 2: defensive
- Spawn 3: defensive
- Spawn 4: offensive
